data.prompt: A dreamy coastal landscape at sunset, with soft waves lapping at the shore while a solitary figure gazes out into the horizon, their silhouette bathed in warm golden light. The pastel hues of pink and lavender blend seamlessly in the sky, evoking a serene sense of longing and introspection.

The comforting glow of the twinkling lights and gentle blues create an atmosphere of tranquility and nostalgia.
